    <div class="region region-content">
     <article about="/node/6907" class="landing-page full clearfix" data-history-node-id="6907" role="article">
      <div class="content">
       <div>
        <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--home-page-carousel paragraph--view-mode--default paragraph--id--2809 carousel slide home-carousel" data-interval="false" data-ride="carousel" id="myCarousel-2809">
         <div class="carousel-inner" role="list">
          <div class="paragraph--layout-slideshow__slide-1 item carousel-item active" role="listitem">
           <div class="row paragraph paragraph--type-home-page-carousel-item paragraph--view-mode-default paragraph--type--home-page-carousel-item paragraph--id--2807 paragraph--color paragraph--color--rgba-dark-blue">
            <div class="container">
             <a href="/fellowships/fellowship-program">
              <div class="paragraph__column row">
               <div class="col-sm-4">
                <div class="tint">
                 <div class="field field--name-bp-image-field field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item">
                  <img alt="Image" class="img-responsive" height="500" src="/sites/default/files/styles/home_page_carousel/public/2019-02/COHEN_red%20city_square.jpg?itok=0an-uQdT" typeof="foaf:Image" width="500"/>
                 </div>
                </div>
               </div>
               <div class="col-sm-8">
                <h3>
                 A center for scholarship
                </h3>
                <p>
                 A residential fellowship program supports innovative, interdisciplinary research into all aspects of Jewish history, thought, and culture, structured around an annual theme.
                </p>
               </div>
              </div>
             </a>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
          <div class="paragraph--layout-slideshow__slide-2 item carousel-item" role="listitem">
           <div class="row paragraph paragraph--type-home-page-carousel-item paragraph--view-mode-default paragraph--type--home-page-carousel-item paragraph--id--2808 paragraph--color paragraph--color--rgba-green">
            <div class="container">
             <a href="/fellowships/fellowship-program">
              <div class="paragraph__column row">
               <div class="col-sm-4">
                <div class="tint">
                 <div class="field field--name-bp-image-field field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item">
                  <img alt="Image" class="img-responsive" height="500" src="/sites/default/files/styles/home_page_carousel/public/2019-02/sanhedrinbig_square.jpg?itok=mw1Q8bEN" typeof="foaf:Image" width="500"/>
                 </div>
                </div>
               </div>
               <div class="col-sm-8">
                <h3>
                 A global hub
                </h3>
                <p>
                 At the Center's core is a residential fellowship program that supports research into all aspects of Jewish history, society, thought, &amp; culture. The fellowship is built around an annual theme designed to stimulate the best new thinking across discipline.
                </p>
               </div>
              </div>
             </a>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
          <div class="paragraph--layout-slideshow__slide-3 item carousel-item" role="listitem">
           <div class="row paragraph paragraph--type-home-page-carousel-item paragraph--view-mode-default paragraph--type--home-page-carousel-item paragraph--id--2823 paragraph--color paragraph--color--rgba-paprika">
            <div class="container">
             <a href="/about-us/library">
              <div class="paragraph__column row">
               <div class="col-sm-4">
                <div class="tint">
                 <div class="field field--name-bp-image-field field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item">
                  <img alt="Image" class="img-responsive" height="500" src="/sites/default/files/styles/home_page_carousel/public/2019-02/93-94%20Hand%20%281%29_square.jpg?itok=I18S_gPw" typeof="foaf:Image" width="500"/>
                 </div>
                </div>
               </div>
               <div class="col-sm-8">
                <h3>
                 A library
                </h3>
                <p>
                 The Library at the Katz Center maintains extraordinary rare book and Judaica holdings, and its visionary librarians are on the forefront of open-access, digital, and collaborative efforts.
                </p>
               </div>
              </div>
             </a>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
          <div class="paragraph--layout-slideshow__slide-4 item carousel-item" role="listitem">
           <div class="row paragraph paragraph--type-home-page-carousel-item paragraph--view-mode-default paragraph--type--home-page-carousel-item paragraph--id--2826 paragraph--color paragraph--color--rgba-fellowship-blue">
            <div class="container">
             <a href="/about-us/publications">
              <div class="paragraph__column row">
               <div class="col-sm-4">
                <div class="tint">
                 <div class="field field--name-bp-image-field field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item">
                  <img alt="Image" class="img-responsive" height="500" src="/sites/default/files/styles/home_page_carousel/public/2019-02/JQR%20Logo_square.jpg?itok=WvaZImhA" typeof="foaf:Image" width="500"/>
                 </div>
                </div>
               </div>
               <div class="col-sm-8">
                <h3>
                 A publishing engine
                </h3>
                <p>
                 From the flagship journal the Jewish Quarterly Review to the Jewish Culture and Contexts book series published with the University of Pennsylvania Press, the Center supports the publication of outstanding scholarship.
                </p>
               </div>
              </div>
             </a>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
          <div class="paragraph--layout-slideshow__slide-5 item carousel-item" role="listitem">
           <div class="row paragraph paragraph--type-home-page-carousel-item paragraph--view-mode-default paragraph--type--home-page-carousel-item paragraph--id--2827 paragraph--color paragraph--color--rgba-gold">
            <div class="container">
             <a href="/education-outreach/katz-center-public-programs">
              <div class="paragraph__column row">
               <div class="col-sm-4">
                <div class="tint">
                 <div class="field field--name-bp-image-field field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item">
                  <img alt="Image" class="img-responsive" height="500" src="/sites/default/files/styles/home_page_carousel/public/2019-02/09-10%20Hasids%20on%20Bicycles_square.jpg?itok=h5DTgGAE" typeof="foaf:Image" width="500"/>
                 </div>
                </div>
               </div>
               <div class="col-sm-8">
                <h3>
                 Twenty-first century learning
                </h3>
                <p>
                 Promoting learning for its own sake, the Center partners with a variety of institutions and uses digital media to make the best scholarship available and meaningful beyond the academy.
                </p>
               </div>
              </div>
             </a>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
          <div class="paragraph--layout-slideshow__slide-6 item carousel-item" role="listitem">
           <div class="row paragraph paragraph--type-home-page-carousel-item paragraph--view-mode-default paragraph--type--home-page-carousel-item paragraph--id--2828 paragraph--color paragraph--color--rgba-orange">
            <div class="container">
             <a href="/fellowships/fellowship-program">
              <div class="paragraph__column row">
               <div class="col-sm-4">
                <div class="tint">
                 <div class="field field--name-bp-image-field field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item">
                  <img alt="Image" class="img-responsive" height="500" src="/sites/default/files/styles/home_page_carousel/public/2019-02/Library%20Books_v2_0_square.jpg?itok=GIPNXut-" typeof="foaf:Image" width="500"/>
                 </div>
                </div>
               </div>
               <div class="col-sm-8">
                <h3>
                 A field builder
                </h3>
                <p>
                 Through mentorship, graduate programs, and support for early-career scholars, the Center is committed to transmitting scholarship across generations and securing a solid foundation for the future of Judaic studies.
                </p>
               </div>
              </div>
             </a>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
         </div>
         <a class="left carousel-control" data-slide="prev" href="#myCarousel-2809" role="button">
          <span aria-hidden="true" class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left">
